Properties.Header: Complete the following and click send to generate an email to the person for who you are requesting to complete FG Students Leader Training videos.

Properties.Name: Person
Properties.Description: The person from whom you are requesting the serving application.

Properties.Name: Custom Message
Properties.Description: A custom message you would like to include in the request.  Otherwise what you see below will be sent.
Properties.DefaultValue:
Hi FG Students Small Group Leaders! 

We are so excited to start small groups back and we know our students are, too. It’s been a very different season that brought more isolation and less interactions, and we are excited to get back to creating a culture of belonging within our student ministry, and a main piece of this is small groups. We will NOT be having our annual Next Gen Volunteer Training due to COVID-19, but we are excited to introduce a series of Volunteer Videos for you to go through on your own, in your own time. Each video is 3-10 minutes long and are on topics that we believe will help you be the best Small Group Leader you can be. Please click the link below (about our FGS Vision), watch the video, and fill out the form when completed. After each submission, you will receive an email to the next one until you get through all 8 videos. Thank you for taking the time to learn more about investing in the next generation!
